a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=26208\">SMP hashing problem</a> by <a href=\"/Robert_Hyatt\" title=\"Robert Hyatt\">Robert Hyatt</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 24, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Shared_Hash_Table#Lockless\" title=\"Shared Hash Table\">Lockless Hashing</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=26211\">SMP search stability</a> by <a href=\"/Jon_Dart\" title=\"Jon Dart\">Jon Dart</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 24, 2009</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010\">2010</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=SMP&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: 2010\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=33700\">SMP basics</a> by <a href=\"/Richard_Allbert\" title=\"Richard Allbert\">Richard Allbert</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 09, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=36082\">SMP speed up</a> by <a href=\"/Miguel_A._Ballicora\" title=\"Miguel A. Ballicora\">Miguel A. Ballicora</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 14, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=36121\">SMP questions</a> by <a href=\"/Harm_Geert_Muller\" title=\"Harm Geert Muller\">Harm Geert Muller</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 19, 2010 </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=38655\">AMD Phenom Hex core (SMP performance problem)</a> by <a href=\"/Miguel_A._Ballicora\" title=\"Miguel A. Ballicora\">Miguel A. Ballicora</a>, 